OL,3,CDelays to housing laws will 'cost
OL,4,Clives', Awaab Ishak's family says
OL,6,FThe law - named after the toddler -
OL,7,Fwill protect social housing tenants
OL,8,Ffrom dangerous hazards and propose
OL,9,Fstrict time limits on councils and
OL,10,Fhousing associations carrying out
OL,11,Frepairs.
OL,13,FBut Deputy Prime Minister and Housing
OL,14,FSecretary Angela Rayner announced on
OL,15,FFebruary 6 that while the law will be
OL,16,Fintroduced in October this year, it
OL,17,Fwill be phased, and some hazards,
OL,18,Fincluding fire and electrical safety,
OL,19,Fwill not be covered until 2027.
