OL,3,CDelays to housing laws will 'cost
OL,4,Clives', Awaab Ishak's family says
OL,6,F"Given the delays that have already
OL,7,Ftaken place, Awaab's parents have
OL,8,Flittle faith that these deadlines will
OL,9,Fbe met - and nothing prevents further
OL,10,Fslippage. To them, this is not in
OL,11,Fkeeping with the urgency of the
OL,12,Fissue," they said.
OL,14,F"They have approached this process in
OL,15,Fextremely good faith, recognising the
OL,16,Fcomplexity of legislative change and
OL,17,Fallowing the government time to
OL,18,Fintroduce a robust, fair, and workable
OL,19,FAwaab's Law.
