OL,3,CDelays to housing laws will 'cost
OL,4,Clives', Awaab Ishak's family says
OL,6,F"Out of respect for the process, they
OL,7,Fchose not to apply pressure, even
OL,8,Fafter the Autumn deadline was missed.
OL,9,FThey trusted that progress was being
OL,10,Fmade. Never did they imagine such
OL,11,Fsignificant delays would follow. Until
OL,12,Fthe day of the government's
OL,13,Fannouncement, they had received no
OL,14,Fprior indication of this.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
