OL,3,CDelays to housing laws will 'cost
OL,4,Clives', Awaab Ishak's family says
OL,6,F"Their frustration is not for
OL,7,Fthemselves, but for the thousands of
OL,8,Ffamilies still trapped in unsafe homes
OL,9,F- families they speak to every day.
OL,10,FThese families cannot afford to wait
OL,11,Findefinitely for protections that
OL,12,Fshould already be in place.
OL,14,F"They also remain deeply concerned
OL,15,Fthat the government is yet to set out
OL,16,Fclear timeframes within which
OL,17,Flandlords must carry out repairs under
OL,18,FAwaab's Law - especially given its
OL,19,Finitial commitment to having the law
OL,20,Fready by Autumn last year.
