OL,3,CDelays to housing laws will 'cost
OL,4,Clives', Awaab Ishak's family says
OL,6,FAwaab's parents are clear: they think
OL,7,Fthese delays will cost lives.
OL,9,FThey urge the public to continue
OL,10,Fsupporting the implementation of
OL,11,FAwaab's Law to ensure it becomes a
OL,12,Freality without further delay.
OL,14,FLast week, Angela Rayner said the
OL,15,Fphased approach "in no way means that
OL,16,Fsocial landlords have any leeway when
OL,17,Fit comes to meeting their existing
OL,18,Fduties to address dangers to health
OL,19,Fand safety".
