OL,3,CDelays to housing laws will 'cost
OL,4,Clives', Awaab Ishak's family says
OL,6,F"Every social housing tenant deserves
OL,7,Fto live in a home that is decent, safe
OL,8,Fand secure and to receive a high-
OL,9,Fquality service from their landlord."
OL,11,FThe government is also planning to
OL,12,Fextend Awaab's Law to the private
OL,13,Frented sector, as part of the Renters
OL,14,FRights Bill which is currently going
OL,15,Fthrough parliament.
OL,17,FRayner said the government will be
OL,18,Fconsulting on how that works in
OL,19,Fpractice "in a way that works for the
OL,20,Fsector and is fair and proportionate
OL,21,Ffor tenants and landlords".
